 century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"historicEvents":[{"id":1705201,"age":27,"year":"1549","julianDay":2286821,"title":"Book of Common Prayer","description":"Book of Common Prayer, a product of the English Reformation, was published in 1549 for assistance in the administration of the sacraments and other rites and ceremonies of the church according to the use of the Church of England. The book outlined morning, evening, and communion prayers and orders for baptism and marriage, thus making England a truly Protestant state.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Book_of_Common_Prayer","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Book of Common Prayer","jurisdictionLevel":1}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes Marche was born in 1522, in Devon, England. She married Richard Marche in 1543, in Devon, England. She died in 1550, in Picardie, France, at the age of 28."},"et":{"1522–1550":"1522–1550","1500–Male":"1500–Surnud","1520–1612":"1520–1612","1514–1583":"1514–1583","1514":"1514","1612":"1612","1522":"1522","1500":"1500","1543":"1543","1520":"1520","1550":"1550","1583":"1583","1549":"1549","Y., Somme, Picardie, France":"Picardie, Prantsusmaa","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"fi":{"1522–1550":"1522–1550","1500–Male":"1500–Kuollut","1520–1612":"1520–1612","1514–1583":"1514–1583","1514":"1514","1612":"1612","1522":"1522","1500":"1500","1543":"1543","1520":"1520","1550":"1550","1583":"1583","1549":"1549","Y., Somme, Picardie, France":"Picardie, Ranska","Devon, England":"Devon, England"},"fr":{"1522–1550":"1522–1550","1500–Male":"1500–Décédé","1520–1612":"1520–1612","1514–1583":"1514–1583","1514":"1514","1612":"1612","1522":"1522","1500":"1500","1543":"1543","1520":"1520","1550":"1550","1583":"1583","1549":"1549","Y., Somme, Picardie, France":"Picardie, France","Devon, England":"Devon, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Agnes Marche est née en 1522, à Devon, Angleterre. Elle a épousé Richard Marche en 1543, à Devon, Angleterre. Elle est décédée en 1550, à P